<bibRefCitation author="New, T. &amp; T. Matsura" pageId="41" pageNumber="40" pagination="93 - 96" refId="ref34151" refString="New, T., and T. Matsura. 1993. A new species of Callistoleon Banks (Neuroptera: Myrmeleontidae). Journal of the Australian Entomological Society 32: 93 - 96, figures 1 - 19." type="journal article" year="1993">New and Matsura 1993: 93-94</bibRefCitation>
